{"id":4423,"content":"<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT size=5 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 由于各种原因，</FONT></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\"><FONT size=5>《炎黄春秋》杂志光盘版的发行日期将再度推迟。对此，特向一直期待获得光盘版的读者朋友致歉。目前本刊正在积极与制作单位沟通，以确定此套光盘版最终的发行时间。一旦确定发行日期，<SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">《炎黄春秋》杂志和炎黄春秋网</SPAN>将在第一时间发布通告。<BR></FONT></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\"><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\"><FONT size=3><FONT size=5>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 已经汇款到本刊发行部邮购光盘版的读者朋友请放心，光盘制作完成后，我们将首先给各位寄出。如果读者朋友有什么问题，可以致电本刊发行部联系，当然也包括先行退款事宜。本刊发行部电话010-68532048或通过编辑部010-68534879转。<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 炎黄春秋发行部<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2009年11月24日<BR></FONT>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<BR><FONT face=黑体><BR>附：</FONT></FONT><FONT size=3><FONT face=黑体>炎黄春秋杂志光盘版简介<BR></FONT><BR></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">这套光盘版首次汇集了《炎黄春秋》杂志自</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\" lang=EN-US>1991</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">年创刊至</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\" lang=EN-US>2007</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">年止在杂志上公开发表过的全部文章，以电子书形式还原《炎黄春秋》杂志</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\" lang=EN-US>17</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">年共</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\" lang=EN-US>204</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">期月刊的原版风貌。文章丰富，图片充实，图文并茂。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">《炎黄春秋》杂志光盘版全套两张，每套售价</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\" lang=EN-US>198</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">元。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\" lang=EN-US><SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </SPAN></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">借此特别声明：</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\">、《炎黄春秋》杂志光盘版属炎黄春秋杂志社发行部独家发行，本社没有委托其它任何单位或个人发行销售此套光盘。</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>\r\n<P style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 